  "texts": [
    "The recent decade has witnessed interesting and magnificent developments.",
    "After enduring the Covid-19 pandemic nightmare, the world is now embracing generative AI.",
    "For some, artificial intelligence is a new challenge following the ordeal, while for others, it heralds the promise of a brighter day.",
    "Artificial intelligence, a branch of computer science that deals with the creation of machines with intelligent behavior, is not a new concept.",
    "AI, or Artificial Intelligence, is dedicated to enhancing machines' capacity to learn, reason, and autonomously make decisions."
  ]
}